message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm happy that you're here to help. I recently submitted a claim for my car insurance, but I haven't heard back yet.
I'm really sorry to hear about the delay in getting back to you. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security?
Certainly, my full name is Sarah Johnson.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah Johnson. Can you now confirm your date of birth?
That's all correct. Can you please provide me with the first line of your address and postcode?
Sure, my address is 123 Oak Street, NW1 4RT.
Great, thank you for the information. Now, could you please confirm your email address?
Of course, my email address is sarah.johnson@email.com.

Thank you for completing security, Sarah. I understand your concern about the delay in your claim. Let me see what I can do to help. One possible resolution could be escalating your claim for urgent review. Does this work for you?
Yes, that sounds good to me. I appreciate your help!
I'm glad we could help. I will go ahead and escalate your claim for urgent review. Thank you for bringing this to our attention. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your quick assistance, Chris!
You are welcome, Sarah! If you need further assistance in the future, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
